# Title: Set Files as System Files Using Attrib.EXE
# Author: frack113
# Date: 2022-02-04
# Level: low
# Description: Detects the execution of "attrib" with the "+s" flag to mark files as system files
# MITRE Tactic: Uncategorized
# Tags: attack.stealth, attack.t1564.001, detection.threat-hunting
# Reference: https://github.com/SigmaHQ/sigma/blob/master/rules-threat-hunting/windows/process_creation/proc_creation_win_attrib_system.yml

CommandLine="* +s *" Image="*\\attrib.exe" OR OriginalFileName="ATTRIB.EXE"